00:22:06.436 --> 00:22:07.978
[BUBBLING]

395
00:22:08.854 --> 00:22:09.855
I got it.

396
00:22:09.855 --> 00:22:12.609
[CREATURE SNARLING]

397
00:22:12.609 --> 00:22:13.776
Holy shit! Holy shit!

398
00:22:15.736 --> 00:22:17.363
